d=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ΕΤΗ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic004363_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2014-09-11, by permission of Museo Archeologico Regionale Paolo Orsi\" src=\"ISic004363_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic004363.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2014-09-11, by permission of Museo Archeologico Regionale Paolo Orsi\" src=\"ISic004363-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic004363_rear_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2014-09-11, by permission of Museo Archeologico Regionale Paolo Orsi\" src=\"ISic004363_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic004363_rear.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2014-09-11, by permission of Museo Archeologico Regionale Paolo Orsi\" src=\"ISic004363_rear-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on autopsy\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Farewell worthy Eukarpia, you lived [--] years\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Other Greek funerary texts from Centuripe, such ISic001397 suggest that \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἔζησες\u003C/span>is most likely in line 4.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Orsi NSA 1907 494 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Letters are plainly cut with minimal serifs on stroke terminations. Alph with straight bar and rounded apex; lunate epsilon and sigma; zeta in form of Z; kappa with full-length arms; rho with fairly large rounded and closed eye.\u003C/p> Line 1-3  19-22  Line 4  15-19  Line 5  13-15  Interlineation line 1 to 3  8-12  Interlineation line 3 to 4  3-5  Interlineation line 4 to 5  10-12  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[251,254,257,260,263,266,269,272],{"id":252,"html":253},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2014-09-11\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐκαρπία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐκαρπία\">Εὐκαρπί[α]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>χρηστ[ὰ] \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>χαῖρ[ε] \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ἔζησ̣[ες] \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ἔτη [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2014-09-11\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/spa